{"tid":157491,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門 豬潤、豬扒撈麵","createTime":"2017-03-15T14:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T13:36:44.000Z","uid":62277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1c2c7fcf0e6d004742775862ad7f5a7d6afc26","tid":157491,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"今日叫左個雙併撈<br />\n豬潤用湯分開上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/220606_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F220606_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=514de8bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/220706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F220706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=165e1e40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我鍾意呢度既豬潤多d<br />\n有咬口、起沙<br />\n而且味濃,無臭味<br />\n湯底鮮甜,味精唔重<br />\n<br />\n豬扒都ok,無落太多梳打粉<br />\n保留到肉味同口感<br />\n微濃,又唔會油<br />\n不過太有咬口既豬扒薄身少少會較好<br />\n<br />\n粗麵麵質一般,下次試下幼麵"},{"pid":"f1c04a63a0f6397dce7e9db27e2185bfbac8062b","tid":157491,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"豬扒睇落無咩肉汁"},{"pid":"35da1da3fad5e478f2df0c26b2e3ca08fd20f098","tid":157491,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"中出巴，成日食好野"},{"pid":"17c09995a05f83f1c0226d31cecd7742b3ad8e04","tid":157491,"uid":49178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:32:32.000Z","msg":"巴打 有係店名<br />\n有興趣想試"},{"pid":"a7f8abcdacc59db475fc0e09d676fdb5b5604a8a","tid":157491,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 有係店名<br />\n有興趣想試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n豬大王<br />\n推介豬潤撈"},{"pid":"d1a62a80304f6d57758487f9bc93b19f